### Using Rest Client to test
### Create Device Log
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/device-logs/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "watering",
  "deviceType": "pump",
  "areaId": 1,
  "note": "Testing device log creation"
}

###

### Create Sensor Record
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/records/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sensorData": {
    "light": 450.2,
    "temperature": 27.5,
    "humidity": 60,
    "soilMoisture": 35
  },
  "areaId": 1,
  "note": "Testing record from HTTP test"
}

###

### Create Schedule

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schedule/create?areaId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "08:30",
  "frequency": ["Monday", "Wednesday", "Friday"],
  "activity": "Auto water plants at morning"
}

